        "name": "Eject Soul",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "Your touch disrupts the connection between body and soul, possibly forcing the soul out of the body altogether. The target must attempt a Fortitude save. You can allow allies to choose the degree of success instead of rolling a saving throw.",
